# lynx
lynx: Local Yard for Notes and eXercises. (A lecture management system)

## Install locally

```bash
pip install -e .
```

For tests:

```bash
pip install -e .[dev]
pytest
```

## CLI usage

```bash
lynx course <course_name>
lynx lecture <lecture_name>
lynx clean
lynx pack
```
